I got a letter from Guerney in reply to mine. He could begin in September.1 What is the next move?

Yours cordially

V. Nabokov





TO: BERNARD GUILBERT GUERNEY1

CC, 1 p.





8 Craigie Circle

Cambridge 38, Mass.

8th February 1944

